{"tid":1155152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有幾多人識慕容公子 Bob叔同佢鬧交有咩用？","createTime":"2019-05-14T18:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T19:11:55.000Z","uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"734b639bb5dca68c03cec7d0105a3bf7d5c3eb62","tid":1155152,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:21:28.000Z","msg":"點解Bob 叔會覺得佢好犀利？其實佢影響唔到其他人。因為身為一個出咗社會做嘢人聽完佢講嘢都知佢戇鳩鳩 同一個弱智仔鬧交有咩用？永遠都覺得佢自己啱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wT0gmds.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwT0gmds.png&h=043d8400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔會幫佢買廣告要link就自己搵<br />\n睇完佢呢條片就知道其實佢冇影響力，真係覺得中學生都唔會理佢。當然佢講得啱有實力嘅人唔讀書係可以賺到錢，但係唔係每個人都有實力。識有人三中開始輟學兩年之後送Pizza每月賺兩三萬，亦都有識人中三開始輟學兩年之後變成一個廢青完全冇出過門口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔多幾年當佢變成一個過氣嘅人物。佢就會知自己錯㗎啦。<br />\nSo don&rsquo;t make stupid people famous<br />\n呢件事最好其實係忽略咗無用公子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs.真係睇Bob叔先知道有呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢而家出名真係要多謝bob叔"},{"pid":"1f81505a549600ed7eae7a3bdb9c0542354befbc","tid":1155152,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2e88b66d19129b8bda866fa025558da78c03402","tid":1155152,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:22:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efe4bfc609f0a5c17983099ac8962984b0649440","tid":1155152,"uid":72597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"義之所為"},{"pid":"17206857ddce39e272b62917434b31113c853d41","tid":1155152,"uid":88279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T19:11:55.000Z","msg":"因為大家細個時都好易比人影響，先唔講佢段片講到咁都有一班人like，你就知佢班fans幾撚蠢下啦，不過都係個句啦，幫得就幫。大家都唔想睇到香港將來個代d人既質素幾低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}